        ],
        "points": 0,
        "text": "Once per battle round, at the start of a phase during your turn, you can select one enemy unit within 18\" of this model. That unit must take a Battle-shock test, subtracting 1 from the test when it does so."
      },
      {
        "id": "harbinger_of_destruction",
